Etymology:
Albanian (*ratsa) rosë f. rosak (m.) ` duck ', rika ` duckling ' corresponds to Slovenian raca, Friulian raze, Romanian raţă, Occitan rit, Finnish sorsa, Sami suorsá, Hungarian réce, Irish (Gaeilge) lacha, Romany ratsoy (m.) ratsa (f.) ` duck '.
For more information see www.geocities.com/protoillyrian